title: The Jersey Barrier - Steady Pace in the Slow Lane [2008]
description:
The Jersey Barrier - Steady Pace in the Slow Lane [2008]

The Jersey Barrier of Athens, GA play slow and sparse, acoustic indie pop, combining the musical roots of previous members of Kincaid (Kindercore), Colfax Abbey (Prospective/TwinTone) and Triangle Park (Kindercore).
